Based On Belief (B.O.B) foreman and multifaceted artiste, BlackMagic recently premiered the music video for his expressive track “Anything For Love”. The video opens with a short message from Blackmagic talking about love, art and sacrifice. Then we are ushered into a very warm and colourful visualization of the North and as the title suggests, it had a general theme of love and acceptance. The artiste expresses himself and his unique sense of style and creativity through out the video with multiple beautiful views and close ups of the setting and his outfits and accessories.. The Spax produced track was shot and directed in Minna, Nigeria by Nakarire Mukoro. Watch “Anything For Love” via YouTube below; 